Package: bbs-client
Version: 0.1.0-alpha
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Jon Kirkpatrick <jon@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/JonKirkpatrick/bbs
Description: Build-a-Bot Stadium Client - Bot orchestration and management UI
 bbs-client is a desktop application for managing bot profiles, orchestrating
 local bot processes, and deploying bots to Build-a-Bot Stadium servers.
 .
 Features:
  - Bot profile management with profile persistence
  - Local bot orchestration (arm/disarm/deploy workflows)
  - Server connectivity and session management
  - Real-time bot status monitoring
  - Plugin catalog browsing and management
Depends: dotnet-runtime-8.0 (>= 8.0) | dotnet-runtime-9.0 (>= 9.0), libgsl0 (>= 2.0)
Standards-Version: 4.6.1
Section: misc
Priority: optional
